{"id":20423,"date":"2019-06-14T23:21:37","date_gmt":"2019-06-14T19:21:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/?page_id=20423"},"modified":"2025-03-19T10:55:23","modified_gmt":"2025-03-19T06:55:23","slug":"al-targhib-wal-tarhib","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-targhib-wal-tarhib\/","title":{"rendered":"Inspiring Hope and Inciting Fear by Imam al-Mundhiri"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Al-Targhi\u0304b wal-Tarhi\u0304b<\/em> (Inspiring Hope and Inciting Fear) is a book of Hadith collected by Imam al-Mundhiri\u0304. It is distinguished because of its inclusion of Hadith besides those found in the Six Books, such as in collections by Imam Ahmad, Al-Tabarani, and Al-Bayhaqi.<\/p>\n<p>The following are some select chapters with English translation and Arabic text.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Book of the Sunnah \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0629<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-sincerity-truthfulness-good-intentions\/\">Sincerity, truthfulness, and good intentions<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-following-book-and-sunnah\/\">Following the Quran and Sunnah<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-bidah-innovations-lowly-desires\/\">Heretical innovations, lowly desires<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Knowledge \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-knowledge-teaching-learning\/\">Seeking knowledge, teaching, and learning<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-acting-upon-knowledge\/\">Acting upon one&#8217;s knowledge<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-arguing-bickering-quarreling\/\">Arguing, bickering, and quarreling<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Ritual Purification \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0647\u0627\u0631\u0629<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-excellent-wudu\/\">Excellent ablution<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-maintaining-renewing-wudu\/\">Maintaining, renewing ablution<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-siwak-miswak-oral-hygiene\/\">Siwak, maintaining oral hygiene<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Prayer \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0644\u0627\u0629<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-the-call-to-prayer\/\">The call to prayer<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-five-salawat\/\">The five prescribed prayers<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-nawafil-salat\/\">Voluntary Sunan prayers<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-salat-al-duha\/\">Forenoon prayer<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-witr-prayer\/\">Witr prayer<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Charity \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u062f\u0642\u0627\u062a<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-paying-zakat\/\">Paying obligatory charity (<em>zakat<\/em>)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-giving-voluntary-charity\/\">Giving voluntary charity<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Fasting \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064a\u0627\u0645<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-virtues-of-fasting\/\">Virtues of fasting<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-fasting-in-ramadan\/\">Fasting in Ramadan<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-fasting-evil-words-deeds\/\">Fasting from evil words and deeds<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Hajj Pilgrimage \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062c<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-ten-days-of-dhul-hijjah\/\">First ten days of Dhul-Hijjah<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of the Recitation of Quran \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0642\u0631\u0627\u0621\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0631\u0622\u0646<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-recitation-quran\/\">Reciting the Quran<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-committing-to-the-quran-reciting-pleasantly\/\">Committing to the Quran, reciting pleasantly<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-surah-al-fatihah\/\">Virtues of Surat al-Fatihah<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-surah-al-baqarah-ali-imran\/\">Surat al-Baqarah and Ali &#8216;Imran<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Remembrance and Supplication \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0643\u0631 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062f\u0639\u0627\u0621<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-dhikr-wa-dua\/\">Remembrance of Allah<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-dua-to-allah\/\">Supplication to Allah<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-istighfar\/\">Seeking forgiveness from Allah<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Judges \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0636\u0627\u0621<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-positions-of-power\/\">Seeking positions of power<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-fearing-oppressor\/\">Supplications when fearing an oppressor<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-bribery-hukm\/\">Evils of bribery in judgment<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-supporting-oppressed\/\">Supporting the oppressed<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-warning-evil-rulers\/\">Warning against support for evil rulers<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Legal Punishments \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u0648\u062f\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-forgiveness-pardon\/\">Forgiveness for criminals and wrongdoers<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Righteousness and Good Relations \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0635\u0644\u0629<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-silat-al-rahim\/\">Good relations with family<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-guarding-rights-of-neighbors\/\">Rights of neighbors<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-on-shuhh-and-bukhl\/\">Greed and miserliness<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-fulfilling-needs-bringing-happiness\/\">Fulfilling needs, bringing happiness<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-visiting-righteous\/\">Visiting Muslims, honoring them<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Book of Manners \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-modesty-haya-shamelessness\/\">Modesty, obscenity, and shamelessness<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-good-character-akhlaq-adab\/\">Good character, morals, and manners<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-kindness-gentleness-hilm\/\">Kindness, gentleness, and forbearance<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-smiles-kalimat-tayyibah\/\">Smiling, cheerfulness, and kind words<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-spreading-greeting-salaam\/\">Spreading peace, greeting with peace<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-shaking-hands-greeting\/\">Shaking hands while greeting<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-withdrawing-trials-tribulations\/\">Withdrawing from trials<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-controlling-anger-rage\/\">Controlling anger, suppressing rage<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-hatred-malice-boycotting\/\">Mutual-hatred, grudges, and boycotts<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-accusing-kufr-takfir\/\">Accusing believers of unbelief (takfir)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-cursing-human-beings-animals\/\">Cursing human beings and animals<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-gossip-rumors-talebearing\/\">Gossip, rumors, and talebearing<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-backbiting-mockery-slander\/\">Backbiting, mockery, and slander<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-reconciliation-between-people\/\">Reconciliation between people<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-guarding-lisan\/\">Guarding the tongue from sins<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-tazkiyyah-qalb-hasad\/\">Purifying the heart from envy<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-humility-vanity-arrogance\/\">Humility, vanity, and arrogance<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-honesty-sidq\/\">Truthfulness and honesty<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-nifaq-two-faces-forked-tongues\/\">Carrying two-faces and hypocrisy<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-none-favored-but-righteousness\/\">None favored but by righteousness<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-removing-harm-roads-pathways\/\">Removing harmful things from road<\/a><